race.description: Thank You Kilcoy Beauty Maiden Plate
race.comment: HELLO PUNTERS (2) sat on the speed from an inside barrier over this trip at Ipswich and only just missed out when the favourite there. This looks an easier race on paper and he maps to be up front again from the good draw. This presents as a great chance to knock over his maiden. PROPAGANDA (5) has trialled impressively coming into this and looks to have plenty of ability. That was over the short course at Toowoomba and the inside gate is ideal for him on debut. Can sit handy and put his best foot forward. JOYFUL CONQUEST (3) gets the senior jockey back on board today and can turn in an improved performance. PRINCE PHOENIX (4) has claims on debut.
